dublin_core.dcvalue: Internet technologies are briefly introduced and those applicable for telemedicine are reviewed Multicast internet technologies are described The National Aeronautics and Space Administration NASA Telemedicine Space bridge to Russia project is described and used to derive requirements for internet telemedicine Telemedicine privacy and Quality of Service QoS requirements are described
Minimally invasive therapy And allied technologies : MITAT : official journal of the Society for Minimally Invasive Therapy
Internet technologies and requirements for telemedicine.
